24:17.690 --> 24:19.715
You know, you're doing just
what I did with smoking.

24:19.858 --> 24:22.520
Doing it because
everyone else does it.

24:22.661 --> 24:24.823
You know something?
You're right.

24:24.964 --> 24:26.762
